data.description: Spacious home with partial canyon view nicely upgraded with new custom paint, new carpet and pad, rehabbed kitchen cabinets with stainless appliances, newer furnace, laminated and tiled flooring plus washer, dryer and refrigerator.  Front bedroom has a view balcony to the canyon as well as master bedroom, master suite has a large closet with mirrored wardrobes. One bedroom and 1/2 bath downstairs. New refinished showers and new toilets.
